text:
Tried the black pepper chicken and original curry chicken puffs. The black pepper chicken is too salty and no peppery taste. The original curry chicken puff is moist but lack curry taste. The folded rim is too thick so it is hard and dry. Price is reasonable at $1.30.
The puffs are made there instead of factory.
Best oyster cake Iâ€™ve had this year. Perfect with the nuts and lightly fried not greasy.
Not sure if this is the one. But the highlight was the fried banana. Curry puff was average to me.
Average puffs which were not expected of a specialist stall
